articles.title: Female cheetah dies in MP's Kuno National Park; third death in 42 days - Deccan Herald
articles.description: A female cheetah died at Madhya Pradesh’s Kuno National Park on Tuesday making it the third death among 20 imported cheetahs that were brought from Namibia and South Africa with the aim of repopulating cheetahs in India nearly 75 years after they became extin…
